name: Skylands: Survival
description:
Hello everyone, here's my first game made in Godot, created for Discord Jam 5!

Assets made by me before the jam started. (I wanted to focus on figuring out Godot, and I say that for the most part, I've got the basics down now!)

Making this was really exciting! I know it's super primitive but I really liked working in Godot. Now I'm really inspired to make more advanced games.
